"'''Return to Tatooine'''" is an article by [[David West Reynolds (real person)|David West Reynolds]] which appeared in [[Star Wars Insider 27|''Star Wars Insider'' 27]]. It deals with Reynolds' treck to North Africa to explore the filming locations for [[Tatooine]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

